<div id="review_3749312957" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3749312957" />
    <a title="Stephanie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/8370061-stephanie"><img alt="Stephanie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1549944100p2/8370061.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3749312957?book_show_action=true">Jan 05, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Stephanie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Stephanie" href="/user/show/8370061-stephanie">Stephanie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8370061-stephanie?shelf=2021">2021</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8370061-stephanie?shelf=january">january</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3749312957" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3606719334292909957">The challenging format and overall pretentious tone overshadow the information to be found within. This is a book for people who are very comfortable in their cooking and tasting skill, and who have the time to experiment and cook -- and want to use the time they have to do so, which may admittedly be a small audience. Interesting as a reference to help with an ingredient you need inspiration for using.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review3749312957">
  <td colspan="2">
    <div class="updateActionLinks">
